snippet: Police arrested two men on Thursday in the case of a teenager who died in April after a suicide attempt that followed months of cyberbullying.
abstract: Canadian police arrest two men in case of Rehtaeh Parsons, teenager who died in April after suicide following months of cyberbullying.
lead_paragraph: Police arrested two men on Thursday in the case of a teenager who died in April after a suicide attempt that followed months of cyberbullying.
